tables.sys_user: ([user_id] INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,[user_name] VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL, [user_pwd] VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, [real_name] VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL, [phone] VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL, [user_icon] VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL DEFAULT NULL, [remark] VARCHAR(512) NOT NULL DEFAULT NULL, [create_time] DATETIME NOT NULL, [create_user] INTEGER NOT NULL, [modify_time] DATETIME NOT NULL, [modify_user] INTEGER NOT NULL, [status] INTEGER NOT NULL)
